ntsync vendored sources
=======================
Upstream Linux NTSYNC driver (the self-contained miscdevice form that
compiles on 5.15 / 6.1 / 6.6). Vendored here so the build no longer fetches
it from an external patch repo. apply_features.sh copies these into
drivers/misc/ntsync.c and include/uapi/linux/ntsync.h and wires Kconfig/
Makefile/defconfig. Upstream author: Elizabeth Figura. GPL-2.0.
